title: New: Retro Culture – Digital
body:
Photo: Daniella Raniti Melbourne’s **Retro Culture** released one of my favourite tracks of last year ([Let’s Make It Work](https://soundcloud.

com/retroculture/lets-make-it-work)), and has now returned with a slight change in direction. Dropping some of the Daft Punk-esque synths, and replacing them with far more chilled out, R&B vibes, bringing his vocals to the forefront, making it more like The Weeknd or SOHN than Get Lucky. Check out Digital below, alongside a couple of older tracks.
